    {
      "id": "5000f70d-c77b-4d4a-88a2-dcb63393d9b1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper presents Moodle Plugins that can be used for analytics purposes and then shows how they can be used at a Faculty in Zagred to interpret student behavior and frame it in the context of student success.",
